</h5>
<div class="problem"><p>Find a basis for the subspace $W$ of $\complex{4}$,
\begin{align*}
W &amp;=
\setparts{\colvector{a + b - 2c\\a + b - 2c + d\\ -2a + 2b + 4c - d\\ b + d}}
